## OpenQASM

**Open Quantum Assembly Language** ( [OpenQASM](/OpenQASM); pronounced *open kazm* ) is, for all intents and purposes, a [programming language](/Programming_language) specifically engineered for the rather niche task of articulating [quantum circuits](/Quantum_circuit) and the [algorithms](/Quantum_algorithm) they embody, destined for the esoteric hardware known as [quantum computers](/Quantum_computing). It’s the closest thing to telling a quantum machine what to do without resorting to shouting at individual [qubit](/Qubit) states.

